   <talk_paragraph index="n087_beggar-accepting" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n087_beggar-accepting-a" mid="7"><![CDATA[<html>Talking about weather is just so common like saying hello. </html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n087_beggar-accepting-b" mid="8"><![CDATA[<html>I’m not trying to be nice. </html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n087_beggar-accepting-c" mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>Can you understand if we talk about something deep? </html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n087_beggar-accepting-d" mid="10"><![CDATA[<html>What do you mean by something deep? </html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="5"><![CDATA[<html>$Ropi the Beggar$<BR>What’s my favorite weather? How stupid are you? Are you trying to be nice? Talk about something deeper! </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n087_beggar-accepting-a" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Ropi the Beggar$<BR>
Common area? Is that the only question you have for me? I’ve travelled around many countries and that is the question you ask me? How pitiful...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n087_beggar-accepting-b" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$Ropi the Beggar$<BR>
You weren’t trying to be nice. Then why are you asking me that stupid question? Well it is obvious that an idiot asks a stupid question. I’ve been to many places that you haven’t been. Ask me where I’ve been if you are going to ask me about the weather. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n087_beggar-accepting-c" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Ropi the Beggar$<BR>Hahaha, insane and stupid are different matters. So don’t think I’m stupid. You may think I’m a bum but I’ve been to everywhere on this continent. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n087_beggar-accepting-d" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>$Ropi the Beggar$<BR>You are going to Lotus Marsh right? Your face expression tells me that you're surprised I know. But you don’t have to ask me that, I’ll tell you why. I know everything about this world. So ask me about your next destination, idiot! </html>]]></talk_question>
